太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站    <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=adea97ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"65b83b53f5e073d06b86d1e609d15243d1f0eaf1","tid":2071003,"uid":315864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f28ce28d40bb760ffb9304940c2ae3c32b7905c7","tid":2071003,"uid":109933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7dff02f870c504311814e2544d0c9b2afe8c1124","tid":2071003,"uid":131125,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"e9fbdc6de9baa45790be2b31469a7f122c079c17","tid":2071003,"uid":315864,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T13:29:28.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />問返佢個姊妹先知係因為我唔應佢 所以佢接受咗第二個男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T13:34:16.000Z","msg":"街市買餸????<br />\n呢檔唔肯搭裸蔥俾我就去第二檔買?<br />\n你條友仲要心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T13:37:42.000Z","msg":"咁樓主自己都同時對兩個女仔有感覺啦 如果瞹味個個話ok你估佢仲會唔會覺得miss 左ex message 好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T08:34:56.000Z","msg":"係一真覺得同個ex好可惜"},{"pid":"0cc63fc9aa15e6ba885747974fc0be01f6f4900a","tid":2071003,"uid":315864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4139674fd58c70dd377f2e8b2ab67becbb04954","tid":2071003,"